# Anchor these to the repo root only. Bare `media` matched ANY path segment
# named media — including web/src/app/api/media/, which silently dropped the
# R2-signing route from every deploy and 404'd all playback. Leading "/" scopes
# each to the top-level folder (the big local media/, model/, supabase/ dirs).
/media
/model
/supabase
*.md
.DS_Store
web/node_modules
web/.next
web/.env*
!web/.env.example
web/scripts/wipe-supabase.mjs
